<h1 id="变量">变量</h1>
<p>强类型和弱类型都可以支持</p>
<h2 id="赋值---强类型">赋值 - 强类型</h2>
<div class="language-go highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">//var 变量名 变量类型 = 值</span> <span class="k">var</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="m">1</span> </code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="赋值---弱类型">赋值 - 弱类型</h2>
<div class="language-go highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">//变量名 := 值</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="m">1</span> </code></pre></div></div>
<p>根据值来判断类型，所以必须初始化</p>
<h1 id="变量类型">变量类型</h1>
<ul> <li>bool</li> <li>string</li> <li>int, int8, int16, int32,...
</li></ul>
